<h2>What is it?</h2>

<p>hi2txt is a utility to convert mame high scores files (hi/nvram) into text
files, for easy integration into Arcade cabinet front-end, leaderboard shared
among friends, etc.<br>
It is heavily inspired from hitotext utility wrote years ago by Fyrecrypts:
huge thanks to him and all related contributors!<br>
If you appreciate the tool, all possible help to support more games and suggest
new features, is warmly welcome, or at least a little thank you (contact:
hi2txt at free.fr) !</p>

<p>[<a title="doc" href="doc/index.html">Documentation</a>] [<b>What's new for the <a href="engine.CHANGELOG.html">engine</a> and the <a href="games.CHANGELOG.html">games</a></b>]</p>

