<h2>Quick Installation Guide for C# version</h2>
<ul>
  <li>DOT.NET Framework 4.5+ must be installed on your Windows</li>
  <li><b>unzip</b> hi2txt@&lt;version&gt;.CSharp.7z</li>
  <li>go inside 'example' folder and double-click on read.bat =&gt; it will
    read a hiscore file and display extracted data. Have a look inside read.bat
    to see the command-line.</li>
</ul>

